data.description: Freshly Updated Modern Farmhouse! This like-new ranch property boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, hardwood floors, a delightful kitchen with a view to the living room, and a covered back patio with a fenced yard for privacy. The neighborhood is thoughtfully designed, complete with sidewalks and pool, and playground. Close to shopping, dining, and entertainment, including North GA Premium Outlets and Hwy 400. Your dream home awaits!
